myo.car.controller

Class Car

  • java.lang.Object
    • myo.car.controller.Car

  • public class Car
extends java.lang.Object
    The Car class is used to represent the Myo Car.

    It includes information on the state of the car, as well as methods that can be used to change the state of the car.
    See Also:
    CarMovingDirection, CarTurningDirection
